<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Internship + Skill Gap Analyzer</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
  <div class="page-wrapper">
    <div class="topbar">
      <div class="logo">✦ Student Portal</div>

      <div class="nav-pill">
        <a href="/" class="active">HOME</a>
        <a href="#">EXPLORE INTERNSHIPS</a>
        <a href="#">MY APPLICATIONS</a>
        <a href="/certificates">ADD CERTIFICATE</a>
        <a href="#">PROFILE</a>
        <a href="/student/register">REGISTER</a>
        <a href="/student/login">LOGIN</a>
        <a href="/student/dashboard">DASHBOARD</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="home-hero">
      <div class="home-hero-content">
        <h1 class="hero-title">Internship + Skill Gap Analyzer</h1>
        <p class="hero-subtitle">
          Track practical experience, manage certificates, build internship readiness,
          and create your student profile for future success.
        </p>

        <div class="home-actions">
          <a href="/student/register" class="btn-primary-glow">Student Register</a>
          <a href="/student/login" class="btn-light-pill">Student Login</a>
          <a href="/certificates" class="btn-light-pill">Upload Certificate</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="page-wrapper">
    <h2 class="section-title">How It Works</h2>
    <p class="section-subtitle">
      A simple student journey from registration to profile building and internship readiness.
    </p>

    <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr)); gap: 20px;">
      <div class="glass-card" style="padding: 24px;">
        <h3 style="margin-bottom: 12px;">1. Create Account</h3>
        <p>Students register through a form and upload their resume for profile building.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="glass-card" style="padding: 24px;">
        <h3 style="margin-bottom: 12px;">2. Complete Profile</h3>
        <p>Add academic background, skills, preferences, and experience details.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="glass-card" style="padding: 24px;">
        <h3 style="margin-bottom: 12px;">3. Track Growth</h3>
        <p>Use the dashboard to manage your student profile and prepare for internships.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>